These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, poppy, daisy
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Flower   | poppy | iris  | rose   | daisy    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

