.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, mauve, lilac, brown
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
2. the person who likes brown is the mexican##1
3. the person who likes lilac is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes mauve##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person who likes lilac##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Color         | brown | lilac   | mauve | white  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

