.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, disaster, adventure, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | family   | adventure | disaster |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

