.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, banana, spinach, asparagus
1. the person eating banana is between the person drinking fanta and the argentine##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
4. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the turkish is between the person eating spinach and the person eating raspberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | coffee  | sprite    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Food           | asparagus      | spinach       | banana   | raspberry      |

