.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, october, september, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, spy, superhero
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is between the german and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Birthday          | october | june  | february   | september    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | spy     | superhero | disaster |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | russian | colombian | german   |

